---
import Hero from "./Hero.astro";
---

<!-- background 100, background 100-->
<section
  class="min-h-screen w-full flex flex-col-reverse lg:flex-row justify-between items-center lg:pl-6 lg:bg-background-50 bg-transparent lg:mb-5"
  id="about"
  data-color="#d1eafa"
  data-color-dark="#051e2e"
>
  <header class="w-full lg:w-4/6 lg:pt-16 flex flex-col">
    <h1 class="text-8xl font-medium hidden lg:inline tracking-tight">
      VALENTIN TT.
    </h1>
    <h2
      class="max-w-max text-5xl bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-600 to-accent-950 dark:from-primary-400 dark:to-primary-700 bg-clip-text text-transparent font-medium my-5 hidden lg:inline tracking-tight"
    >
      Software Developer.
    </h2>
    <p
      class="max-w-4xl lg:pr-10 xl:pr-52 lg:pt-6 px-5 lg:px-0 p-3 lg:py-0 mx-3 sm:mr-16 mt-5 lg:mx-0 border border-text-500 lg:border-0 rounded-lg shadow-[2.0px_4.0px_4.0px_rgba(0,0,0,0.10)] lg:shadow-none z-10 bg-background-50 lg:bg-transparent"
    >
      Hey there! ðŸ‘‹ I'm Valentin TT, a
      <span
        class="font-semibold text-emerald-600 dark:first-letter:text-emerald-400 italic"
        >Full-stack</span
      > Web Developer who loves working with
      <span class="font-semibold text-pink-500 italic">React</span>. I'm all
      about learning through teamwork and collaboration! I strongly believe that
      when we work together, creativity thrives. Communication is key to keep
      learning and growing.
    </p>
    <p
      class="max-w-4xl lg:pr-10 xl:pr-52 lg:pt-6 px-5 lg:px-0 py-3 lg:py-0 mx-3 sm:ml-16 my-5 lg:mx-0 border border-text-500 lg:border-0 rounded-lg shadow-[2.0px_4.0px_4.0px_rgba(0,0,0,0.10)] lg:shadow-none z-10 bg-background-50 lg:bg-transparent"
    >
      Beyond web development, I'm into cybersecurity, reverse engineering,
      electronics, and contributing to <span
        class="font-semibold text-accent-700 italic">open-source</span
      > projects. Exploring these, not only adds to my skills but also keeps my
      excitement alive for solving problems and coming up with new ideas.
    </p>
  </header>
  <Hero />
</section>
<style>
  p {
    font-size: clamp(0.5rem, 0.7rem + 0.4vw, 1.375rem);
    text-wrap: stable;
  }
</style>
